msgstr "Zadana mapa za odabir prilikom izvoza videa"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:257
msgid "Values"
msgstr "Vrijednosti"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:259
msgid "**Recent Folder**"
msgstr "**Nedavna mapa**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:259
msgid ""
"The last folder used for this same operation. Project folders, Import "
"folders, and Export folders are tracked separately."
msgstr ""
"Zadnja mapa korištena za istu operaciju. Mape projekata, uvoza i izvoza "
"prate se zasebno."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:260
msgid "**Project Folder**"
msgstr "**Mapa projekta**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:260
msgid ""
"The current project folder (or the user's home folder, if the project is not "
"yet saved)"
msgstr ""
"Trenutna mapa projekta (ili korisnička početna mapa, ako projekt još nije "
"spremljen)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:266
msgid "Reset (Default Values)"
msgstr "Resetiraj (zadane vrijednosti)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:268
msgid ""
"To reset **all** preferences to their default values, please delete the "
"``openshot.settings`` file and re-launch OpenShot. The settings file can be "
"located at this path: ``~/.openshot_qt/openshot.settings`` or ``C:"
"\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\openshot.settings``. When OpenShot is re-"
"launched, it will create the missing ``openshot.settings`` file with default "
"values."
msgstr ""
"Za resetiranje **svih** postavki na zadane vrijednosti, molimo obrišite "
"datoteku ``openshot.settings`` i ponovno pokrenite OpenShot. Datoteka "
"postavki može se nalaziti na putanji: ``~/.openshot_qt/openshot.settings`` "
"ili ``C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\openshot.settings``. Kada se "
"OpenShot ponovno pokrene, stvorit će nedostajuću datoteku ``openshot."
"settings`` sa zadanim vrijednostima."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:273
msgid ""
"Optionally, you can delete the entire ``.openshot_qt/`` folder and re-launch "
"OpenShot. However, please make a **backup** of any customized folders: "
"**emojis, presets, profiles, recovery, title_templates, transitions, or "
"yolo**. For example, your ``/recovery/`` sub-folder contains backup copies "
"of all your existing projects (``*.osp`` files)."
msgstr ""
"Opcionalno, možete obrisati cijelu mapu ``.openshot_qt/`` i ponovno "
"pokrenuti OpenShot. Međutim, molimo napravite **sigurnosnu kopiju** bilo "
"kojih prilagođenih mapa: **emojis, presets, profiles, recovery, "
"title_templates, transitions ili yolo**. Na primjer, vaša podmapa ``/"
"recovery/`` sadrži sigurnosne kopije svih postojećih projekata (``*.osp`` "
"datoteke)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:278
msgid ""
"Deleting the ``.openshot_qt/`` folder is the quickest method to restore "
"OpenShot preferences and settings to their Default values (i.e. also called "
"a `clean install`). When OpenShot is re-launched, it will create any missing "
"folders (i.e. ``.openshot_qt/``) and settings files. See our `step-by-step "
"guide <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Clean-Installation-of-"
"OpenShot>`_ for more information about **clean installs** of OpenShot."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje mape ``.openshot_qt/`` najbrži je način za vraćanje OpenShot "
"postavki i podešavanja na njihove zadane vrijednosti (tzv. `čista "
"instalacija`). Kada se OpenShot ponovno pokrene, stvorit će sve nedostajuće "
"mape (npr. ``.openshot_qt/``) i datoteke s postavkama. Pogledajte naš `korak-"
"po-korak vodič <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Clean-"
"Installation-of-OpenShot>`_ za više informacija o **čistim instalacijama** "
"OpenShota."
